Hi Zach,

Could you please refund:

5,000 for the rental from 29/08 to 2nd of October (see rent summary =
attached),=20

=EF=BF=BC
298.74 for the Water rates for the rented accommodation
=EF=BF=BC
395.85 for the vets (please find attached the Vets notes and the =
transaction record on my bank account
=EF=BF=BC=EF=BF=BC


Thanks and regards,
Raffaella

> On 2 Sep 2025, at 11:28=E2=80=AFAM, Claims <Claims@tower.co.nz> wrote:
>=20
> Good afternoon, Raffaella.
> =20
> It was good talking to you today.
> =20
> To recap our conversation.
> You will receive the contents settlement in three to five days
> You will receive the stress benefit payment of $2,000 in the same time =
period.
> You are to send us your vet fee and report for the cats being hurt =
from the claimed event.
> I will update you on a monthly basis at the beginning of each month.
> You would like your claim file from the date of loss to today to be =
sent to you. I will get this actioned for you.
> You will send me privacy requests for new information we have on file =
including new claim notes from today onwards.
> =20
> Kind regards,
> =20
> Zach
> =20
