<div lang=3D"EN-US" link=3D"#000000" vlink=3D"purple" =
style=3D"word-wrap:break-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1"><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good afternoon, =
Raffaella.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p =
class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">It was good talking =
to you today.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p =
class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">To recap our =
conversation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ul style=3D"margin-top:0in" type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l0 =
level1 lfo1"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You will receive the =
contents settlement in three to five days<o:p></o:p></span></li><li =
class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 =
lfo1"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You will receive the stress =
benefit payment of $2,000 in the same time =
period.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" =
style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You are to send us your vet fee and report =
for the cats being hurt from the claimed =
event.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" =
style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I will update you on a monthly basis at the =
beginning of each month.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li =
class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 =
lfo1"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You would like your claim file =
from the date of loss to today to be sent to you. I will get this =
actioned for you.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" =
style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You will send me privacy requests for new =
information we have on file including new claim notes from today =
onwards.
<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p =
class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Kind =
regards,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p =
class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Zach =
