></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">Just=
 letting you know that I=E2=80=99ve processed the settlement to your =
nominated account, as confirmed by you, covering the temporary =
accommodation and cleaning costs to date.</span><span =
style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p=
></o:p></span></p>
