<div><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">&nbs=
p;</span><span =
style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p=
></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">I =
will appear in your account as two separate payments one for the =
temporary accommodation and the other for cleaning costs.</span><span =
style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p=
></o:p></span></p>
</div>
