<div><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">Plea=
se reply to this email for any further costs incurred for either the =
Contents or the Temporary Accommodation as both will be paid under this =
Contents claim as is the higher
 of the two benefits for Temporary Accom</span><span =
style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p=
></o:p></span></p>
</div>
